{{#modal-dialog onClose="closeModal"}}
  <h3 class="modal__title">Recording Levels</h3>

  <div class="modal__content">
    <p>
      Each recording option includes professional quality digital audio and video files for you to download.
      CDs and DVDs are also available.
    </p>

    <h4>Multi Camera - <span class="light">$225/hour</span></h4>
    <p>
      A multi camera shoot is prefect for those seeking a truly professional recording. It incorporates three 
      different camera angles and professional audio for a recording that will capture every aspect of your
      performance.
    </p>

    <h4>Single Camera - <span class="light">$150/hour</span></h4>
    <p>
      This is great option for those seeking an archival or audition recording. The camera will capture your 
      entire performance from the audience perspective.
    </p>
    
    <h4>Audio Only - <span class="light">$100/hour</span></h4>
    <p>
      Capture you're performance with the highest quality audio recording. This is a great option for those who
      don't require video.
    </p>

    <p class="text-center">
      {{#link-to 'recordings' (query-params demo=true) class="btn btn-primary"}}See examples{{/link-to}}.
    </p>
  </div>
{{/modal-dialog}}
